Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:55.09,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}満開の愛を載せて　笑顔  届きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:05.70,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新しい世界の始まり　My Dear　Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:11.71,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,イージーだった私に　論外全部サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.37,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}後悔なんで　もうしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:23.45,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな困難なことも　ハッピーに変換したら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:29.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝日も手招きしているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.23,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,不安にこっそり震えてても強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,胸　ギュッと振り絞ったら加速して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:41.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,勇気感じる　だって君がすぐ傍に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:47.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一緒にどこまでも　進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:54.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乗っちゃった追い風に　精一杯　届けたいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}君へと繋ぐココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:07.09,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}最新のコラムに　めいいっばい　気持ち込めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:15.91,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}ときめいて　どこでも行けるよ　My Dear　My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:55.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}載上盛放的愛  希望笑容能夠送達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:05.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}新世界的開始  My Dear  Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:11.71,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經安逸的我  告別所有的不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.37,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}已經不會再後悔了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:23.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎樣的困難  也要設法變成快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:29.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Shine  朝陽也在招手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.23,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,不安時偷偷地顫抖也要逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:35.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,揪緊了心一口氣全力加速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:41.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了勇氣  因為你就在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:47.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}一起走遍天涯海角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:54.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}乘上了愛之風  竭盡全力去傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}和你相連的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:07.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}在最新的新聞欄裡  將所有的心情都傾注進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:15.91,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}心跳不已  無論何處都能前往  My Dear  My Dear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡…歡迎大家回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  秋老虎說的就是這個時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:22.90,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(543,405)\fad(500,0)}第一次的、思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼～呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起  小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小屁屁～小胸部～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放·開·我·啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我自重點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～但是～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別用筷子指人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是但是但是～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得胸部也被摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是～那可是絕無僅有的良機～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  小屁屁～小胸部～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好嗎  多虧小遙墊在下面你才沒受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明救了我  我卻連聲謝謝都沒說  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小佳奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的不是佳奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你也太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是天真  佳奈是溫柔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希對不起啦  給優希也摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  佳奈為什麼要爬樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  因為太熱  就忍不住…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且文太也在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼太熱就要爬樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是奶奶教我的  貓知道哪裡涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我也知道  球藻說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問  球藻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是北海道出身所以叫球藻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  我是問那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻姐就是…我想想  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是去年還在這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是風新開業以來的廢柴員工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風新開業以來的…廢柴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙被狗咬住  然後扯壞了之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看錯了名字  把報紙送錯之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是家常便飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為迷路  報紙很晚才送到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客戶來投訴  我都不知道過幾次歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順便因為回來得也很晚  急著做早飯的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把文太的貓罐頭當成青花魚罐頭開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  她根本就沒回得來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以老要人去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  我還自己回得來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  代理可是挺開心的～喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小球藻在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有  有什麼好開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  雖然嘴上碎碎唸個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻經常跟她黏在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要跟那種磨人的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是越磨人的孩子越可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無稽之談！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像惹代理生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦  她只是鬧彆扭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起來～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還記得不  去年春天下大雪那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得記得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大雪是指那次十八年一遇的大寒流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  那一天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  好慘好慘  在街上連人帶車地摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事倒是沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道又是球藻姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有讓她帶上手機出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都掛在她脖子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼不夠  晨報還是體育報？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我愛  請給我愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了  冷靜啊代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去接球藻姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  今天我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪裡走很辛苦的  又危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  今天我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且說不定球藻姐會打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡還是留個人在比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢  你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在天神附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猜對了  能拜託你個事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優希那邊我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  也讓小遙來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我愛  請給我愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像會很麻煩  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是球藻姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日記！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻掉到河裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  一般都會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也急了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說了交給我  結果還是打了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  雛田？找到姐姐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理  不妙啊  球藻姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  是不是應該叫警察來？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理？喂  你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理  代理！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  是雛田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小球藻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  看樣子她剛走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑一跑應該能追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那代理就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛  不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻姐吧  其實我現在正…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  是小貓不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻的小貓朋友少了一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢  總之你先回店裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我馬上跟優希匯合後就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了告訴她找到球藻的圍巾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理跑得還真快～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲妃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是擔心死啦  剛才聽小遙說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理居然像那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說～嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平時那麼不坦率的代理居然說「我很擔心啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坦率的代理太美～了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙  扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  代理有在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼嘛  又不是什麼好害羞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雛田也扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一樣  都扣薪水扣薪水扣薪水！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然扣薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很過分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  慶祝佳奈也被扣薪水  用大米可樂乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  球藻真是好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她會用能讓代理變坦率的魔法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法啊  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想學～啊  那個魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  就能隨時隨地跟坦率的代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小遙遙  快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  如果不是魔法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理為什麼能在球藻面前那麼坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是發生了什麼我們不知道的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈覺得是發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是把圍巾給了貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻一定非常溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  大家也都這麼溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  那還真是稀奇～啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確  代理很少那麼坦率的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指由小球藻去接代理這件事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  球藻姐總是迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是她第一次接別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻那之後很快就畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是第一次也是最後一次接人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  真是太好了～啊  小球藻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後的最後  終於沒讓人去接她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊  那時候準確來說應該是代理去接她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是～啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是有點口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  佳奈也口渴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  老盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理不覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,球藻從這裡畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是覺得折騰人的傢伙走了  輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  代理不是對球藻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:20:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我跟大家分開了的話  一定會很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈你有一天也是會離開這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  我也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有兩個小時就該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是天神的小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為在原來的地方沒看到它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就到處找了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我們才到處找了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天就走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,房間收拾好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  咲妃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是自己找到這裡來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話  「第一次的、減肥？」
